			<h1>Agenda</h1>
			<div id='calendar'></div>
			<div class='big-bg row' id='open'>
				<div class="col-md-6"></div>
				<div class="col-md-6"><div class="col-md-12">
					<h1>Opening Ceremony</h1>
						<ul><li>Place：College of Medicine</li>
								<li>Topic：Tainan・Connection・Gung ho<br/>
										Every team have to fill their answers in the registration form before participating. We will show their expectations and prospects on screen duing the opening ceromoney with video.(Reference: 0:00~0:20, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tw9QirLbFXQ" target="_blank">MaD Asia 2015</a>) With this, people from different countries will interlinked an get to know each other better.<br/>
								<blockquote><Every team have to fill their answers in the registration form><br/>
								Long time ago, There's a guy from_____, he brought____to this town. The first thing he saw was_____.<br/>
								The extraordinary scenery about this place is that_____. He would like to find out_____, and bring_____back.</blockquote></li></ul>
				</div></div>
			</div>
