				<div class="col-md-4 col-md-height col-md-middle"><img src="/images/2016conf/webneed-06.png"/></div>
				<div class="col-md-6 col-md-height col-md-top">
					<h1>Evening Party</h1>
					<ul class="row">
						<li class="col-md-6">
							<h2>Buffet</h2>
							<p>The iGEM 2016 Conference will kick off with scrumptious local delicatessen and cuisine. All teams are advised not to be shy to communicate with each other in order to warm up for the long presentation marathon the next day.</p>
						</li>
						<li class="col-md-6">
							<h2>Talent Show</h2>
							<p>Every team have to perform a talent show within 5 minutes during the opening ceremony. With buffet dinner and the show, we will get to know each other well with their very own enthusiasm and specialities, which will be a start for 2016 iGEM Asia-Pacific Conference at Tainan, Taiwan.<br/>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-1"></div>
			</div></div>
