			</div>
			<div class="row" id='team-proj'><div class="row-md-height">
				<div class="col-md-1"></div>
				<div class="col-md-4 col-md-height col-md-middle"><img src="/images/2016conf/webneed-07.png"/></div>
				<div class="col-md-6 col-md-height col-md-top">
					<h1>Team's Project ＠College of Medicine</h1>
					<ul class="row">
						<li class="col-md-6">
							<h2>Team presentations </h2>
							<p>The team presentation will host by professors and representatives of our sponsor. This presentation is about topics which is going to be presented at iGEM Giant jamboree 2016. It is 20 minutes long English presentation, content includes present and future research and planning, and of course 20 minutes Q&A session (iGEM 2016 competition format).</p>
						</li>
						<li class="col-md-6">
							<h2>Poster Exhibitions</h2>
							<p>Brief introduction:<br/>
								 There'll be a 20 minutes break in between every team presentations for poster exhibitions. the purpose of this program is to enable every team to share their research works and findings.</p>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-1"></div>
			</div></div>
