				<div class="col-md-1"></div>
				<div class="col-md-4 col-md-height col-md-middle"><img src="/images/2016conf/webneed-08.png"/></div>
				<div class="col-md-6 col-md-height col-md-top">
					<h1>Round Table</h1>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-6">
							<p>Brief introduction:<br/>
								 Host by professors or representatives of entrepreneus to lead the participants to think out of the box. Most people might get the wrong idea but this program is carried out through sharing not debating. By connecting different point of views and thoughts of the participants, we can create a whole new idea.<br/>
							<table class="table table-bordered"><tr><td>25 tables</td>
												 <td>4 topics</td>
												 <td>3 rounds</td>
												 <td>150 minutes</td></tr></table>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6">
							<h2>Topic</h2>
							<span style="font-size:18px">5 main topics, can be set by entrepreneur or teachers</span>
							<ul><li>International issue
										<ul><li>Global air pollution issues</li></ul>
									</li>
									<li>Biology
										<ul><li>Genetically modified goods</li></ul>
									</li>
									<li>Ethics
										<ul><li>Medical Ethics</li>
												<li>Bioethics</li></ul>
									</li>
									<li>Environment
										<ul><li>Economy and environment</li></ul>
									</li>
									<li>Energy
										<ul><li>Biotechnology towards sources of energy</li></ul>
									</li></ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-1"></div>
			</div></div>
