				<div class="col-md-1"></div>
				<div class="col-md-4 col-md-height col-md-middle"><img src="/images/2016conf/webneed-09.png"/></div>
				<div class="col-md-6 col-md-height col-md-top">
					<h1>iGEM Experience Sharing Workshop</h1>
					<ul class="row">
						<li class="col-md-6">
							<p>Brief introduction:<br/>
								 Next, World cafe session. Each table there'll be a member of iGEM NCKU_Tainan leading other participants to share their iGEM experience. throughout their iGEM journey, we can all improve to be better and also learn from our failures and mistakes which bring no harm to every teams. </p>
						</li>
						<li class="col-md-6">
							<p>Divided into two parts:
								<ul><li>Light up：<br/>
												Share positive stories, experiences, uniqueness, management tips, etc so that other teams can reffered to.</li>
										<li>Fucked up：<br/>
												Share failures and downfall of own team in order to allow other teams to learn from mistakes, to understand that story has an ending but in life, every ending is a new beginning. If any of the teams have difficulties, they can speak out too so that others can help to think for a solution.</li></ul>
							</p>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-1"></div>
			</div></div>
