											<li>Li-Hsing Campus: Faculty of Taiwanese Literature, the Magical School of Green Technologies</li>
											<li>Kuang-Fu Campus: Banyan Tree Garden, the Cheng-Kung Pond, Gate Jing-Po(one of the west gate among the others 14 gates built by the Tainan Governmanet during Qing Dynasty)</li>
											<li>Tzu-Chiang Campus: Faculty of Mechanical Engineering, Electrical Engineering, Chemical Engineering and Science-Technology Building</li>
											<li>Cheng-Kung Campus: Main Library, Museum of History</li></ul>
								</li></ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-1"></div>
			</div></div>
