						<ul><li>Award Ceremony<br/>
										Giving out certificates and trophies, professors and representatives of entrepreneus are invited to conclude the overall academic exchange conference. And local products of Tainan will be giving out as souvenirs.</li>
								<li>Farewell Dinner<br/>
										As the closure of the conference, all professors, teachers, particiants, etc. are invited to have the last farewell dinner. This will be the starting point of the road to the MIT platform.</li></ul>
					</p>
				</div></div>
